txt.en: You have encountered the threatening Tumoz the Fume. From its home on the slopes of Mount Doom, the beast patrols the battle plains for intruders.
Tumoz the Fume can be found patrolling The Wastes.\n\nYou have encountered Tumoz the Fume and should defeat the beast for those who brave these harsh lands.
You have defeated Tumoz the Fume.
